---

<section class="payperuse" id="pricing-model">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-headline" style="text-align:center;">
      Every Message Has a Price.<br />Every Price Has a Receipt.
    </h2>

    <!-- Flow diagram -->
    <div class="flow">
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="flow-label">Customer sends message</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&rarr;</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="flow-label">AI thinks</div>
        <span class="cost-badge">$0.005</span>
        <div class="flow-tx">Stellar TX: 0.005 USDC</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&rarr;</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="flow-label">Catalog lookup</div>
        <span class="cost-badge">$0.001</span>
        <div class="flow-tx">Stellar TX: 0.001 USDC</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-arrow">&rarr;</div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="flow-label">Reply sent</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key cost stats -->
    <div class="cost-grid">
      <div class="cost-stat">
        <span class="cost-number">$0.005</span>
        <span class="cost-desc">One AI response</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-stat">
        <span class="cost-number">$0.001</span>
        <span class="cost-desc">One catalog query</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-stat">
        <span class="cost-number">$0.03</span>
        <span class="cost-desc">Avg full conversation</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cost-stat">
        <span class="cost-number">$30</span>
        <span class="cost-desc">1,000 conversations/mo</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-callout">
      <p>A human sales rep costs <strong>$1,200/month</strong>. Vendly handles the same volume for <strong>$30</strong>. And it never sleeps.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .payperuse {
    background: var(--navy-light);
  }

  .flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 48px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .flow-step {
    background: var(--navy);
    border: 1px solid var(--navy-lighter);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 140px;
    flex: 0 1 auto;
  }

  .flow-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .flow-tx {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--purple-light);
    align-self: center;
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .flow-arrow {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .cost-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 48px auto;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cost-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  .cost-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cost-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
  }

  .cost-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gray-400);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .comparison-callout {
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--gray-200);
  }
</style>
